            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Frustrated with expensive and outdated ground school options"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "level": 2,
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Pain Points"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "unordered-list",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Ground school costs $400\u2013$800 and materials go stale quickly"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Practice exams don't reflect actual test difficulty or DPE oral exam style"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "list-item",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "No access to experienced pilots for advice without paying premium consulting fees"
